title: These Bert Show Members Recap One Of The Greatest Nights Of Their Lives
description:
This past week was huge for Moe, Romeo, and Keity. They hosted their first ever live podcast of "In The Moement." Leading up to the day, Rome opened up about his anxiety.
How did he handle the night? We have an update!
